com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.util
Class Logger

java.lang.Object
  com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.util.Logger

public final class Logger
extends Object

A class which wraps the Android.util.Log class, providing a central point to enable or disable the library's logging and customise the logging tag.

By default, logging is enabled and the logging tag is set to the value of com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.TAG.

Author:
mcaunter
See Also:
Constants.TAG
